<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id056eeebc-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d" identifier="/us/usc/t19/s1649"><num value="1649">§ 1649.</num><heading> Change in designation of customs attachés</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">On and after <date date="1930-06-17">June 17, 1930</date>, customs attachés shall be known as “Treasury attachés.”</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id056eeebd-3a70-11f1-8ace-823fb135378d">(<ref href="/us/act/1930-06-17/ch497">June 17, 1930, ch. 497</ref>, title IV, § 649, <ref href="/us/stat/46/762">46 Stat. 762</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
